full_text: On this the 22 State of CALIFORNIA day of January 19 79 , before me, SS. County of LOS ANGELES the undersigned Notary Public, personally appeared SOCORRO A. RAMIREZ known to me to be the person(s) whose name(s) is subscribed OFFICIAL SEAL OR Maria Teresa Ramirez to the within instrument and acknowledged that she RES NOTARY PUBLIC - CALIFORNIA executed the same for the purposes therein contained. PRINCIPAL OFFICE IN CHICAGO LOS ANGELES COUNTY IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I hereunto set my hand and official seal. My Commission Expires Mar. 5, 1982 Maria MARIA Therese TERESA RAMIREZ Basing GENERAL ACKNOWLEDGEMENT FORM
